[test coref]
# Generation 22: minimal discourse coreference for unary factual turns.
> he is a pilot
< I don't know who he refers to.
> dana is a pilot
< Learned: pilot(dana).
> she is a teacher
< Learned: teacher(dana).
> is she a pilot?
< Yes.
> she is not a robot
< Learned: not robot(dana).
> is her a robot?
< No.
> what do you know about her?
< dana is a pilot; dana is a teacher; dana is not a robot.
> why is she a teacher?
< teacher(dana) is a known fact.

